\ip \bd ?Pa r…®m…®rai n…ôkw…ôkw…ô e?\bd* Keinein m…ô pa nhag…®n r…®m…®rai n…ôkw…ôkw…ô e- n…ômehu…ô kupan kape nim…ôhuak k…®mnhani mham…ô Luk r…®m…®rai n…ôkw…ôkw…ô e. In p…ôh nien m…ô yermam…ô twelef k…®rik kape Yesu, m…ôr…®g in r…®rkun huv…ô aposol Pol, k…®ni mam…ôriw…ôk-p…ôn rehu…ô tuk Pol. P…ôh nien m…ô Luk yem…ô Isrel, m…ôr…®g in yem…ô Gris; m…ôr…®g in yem…ôhuak k…®rik. In dokta kape nor-huv…ôyen narmam…ô, k…®ni mor huv…ô skul. M…®w…ôs huv…ô n…ôvsaoyen kape nar…®mnar yame r…®mat…ôrhav ye nar…ôyen kape Yesu. In r…®m…®rai n…ôkw…ôkw…ô e, m…®ne Wok yame Aposol m…®n…ô K…®m…®sor.  
\ip \bd ?R…®m…®rai ramv…ôn k…®mi pa?\bd* R…®m…®rai n…ôkw…ôkw…ô e ramv…ôn k…®mi in k…®rik, nhag…®n e Teofilas. N…®prai nhag e ramni m…ô, ‚ÄúYermam…ô yame rorkeikei Kughen.‚Äù Luk r…®m…®rai n…ôkw…ôkw…ô e ramv…ôn k…®mi kw…ôn a, m…ôr…®g r…®rkun m…ô n…ôm…ôhuak m…®n…ô khapsaah tuks…ôvhek…®n.  
\ip \bd ?N…®mraghien r…®mnhawor p…ôn iran m…®ne ye n…®p…®g yame r…®m…®rai?\bd* Ye n…®p…®g a, n…ôvsaoyen kape Yesu rehu…ô m…ôr…ôrao. Kas…ôr…®g, t…®ks…®n k…®mnhani n…ôfrak…®sien iran, t…®ks…®n k…®mnhaukreik…®n n…ôvsaoyen kape Yesu mhani atuk ye n…ôr…®gien kap…ôri…ô.  
\ip \bd ?R…®m…®rai n…ôkw…ôkw…ô e tuk naha?\bd* Luk rorkeikei m…ô tukr…®ni atuatuk n…ôgkiarien ye nar…ôyen kape Yesu. R…®m…ô tukr…®rkun huv…ô n…ôfrak…®sien ye nar…ôyen kape Yesu, mam…ôgkiar k…®mi narmam…ô yam…ô m…®ne k…®mnas…ôriw…ôk iri…ô Yesu mas…ôm naha nhag…®n yame In r…®mnamor. K…®ni Luk r…®m…®w…ôs huv…ô n…ôgkiarien kap…ôri…ô, kwas…®g ik…®n r…®rai n…ôkw…ôkw…ô e. In rorkeikei m…ô tukrhajoun m…ô Yesu In yermam…ô …ôfrak…®s k…®rik m…®ne Kughen, r…®m…®p…ôh norien nar has k…®rik. In Kughen, k…®ni In rav…ôh m…®ragh narmam…ô.  
