\v 1-3 Teofilas, ik yamehu…ô k…®rik, kamsiai ik. Narmam…ô khapsaah k…®m…®s…ôm nar…®mnar k…®n n…®mr…®ri…ô yame Yesu r…®mnor ye n…®p…®g r…®mnamar…ô ye tokrei tan…ô. Iri…ô k…®mn…®sar…ô ye n…®p…®g kape n…®rikakunien kape nar…®mnar m…®n…ô a, k…®ni m…®sarkut p…®k m…ô tuks…ôr…ôhu atuatuk n…ôvsaoyen kape nar…®mnar m…®n…ô a.\x - \xo 1:1-3 \xt Wok 1:1 \x* K…®mnharai ta nar…®mnar yam…ô m…®ne narmam…ô t…®ks…®n k…®mnhani, k…®ni mhani-…ôrhav. K…®ni yo y…®m…®w…ôs huv…ô n…ôgkiarien iran m…®n…ô m…ô jak…®rkun huv…ô nar…®mnar m…®n…ô a ye n…®rikakunien kafan. K…®ni takt…ôkun ai, kafak n…ôr…®gien r…®m…ô jakrai atuatuk nar…®mnar m-fam mher-pre k…®n. Jakrai atuatuk yam…ô m…®n…ô k…®m…®s…ôkup…ôn, m…®ne yam…ô m…®ne k…®mnhakwas…®g.\fig Luk ramrai n…ôkw…ôkw…ô kafan|alt="Luke writing on a scroll" src="Write_d.jpg" size="col" loc="Bottom left" copy="Urs Wegman" ref="LUK 1:1-3" \fig*  
\v 4 Y…®mnorkeikei m…ô jakni nar…®mnar m…®n…ô e tuk ik m…ô tak…®rkun atuatuk n…ôfrak…®sien kape n…ôvsaoyen yame k…®nhajoun ta ik k…®n.   
\s1 Agelo k…®rik r…®m…®ni-…ôrhav narhayen kape Jon Baptaes  
\p
\v 5 Ye n…®p…®g king kape provins e Judia, nhag…®n e Herod Ehu…ô, pris k…®rik aik…®n, nhag…®n e Sekaraea. In k…®rik ye pris m…®n…ô kamokr…ôn k…®n …ôri…ô k…®m…ô, ‚ÄúPris m…®n…ô kape kw…ôn…ôr…ôus kape Apia,‚Äù [yame r…®mas…®-p…ôn ye kw…ôn…ôr…ôus kape Eron kup…ôn]. Kafan piahwaru, nhag…®n e Elisabet, r…®mas…®-p…ôn m…®n ye kw…ôn…ôr…ôus kape pris e Eron.  
\v 6 K…®ni iriu kw…ôtuatuk ye n…®mr…® Kughen, maw…ôri-p…ôn huv…ô norien kape Loa kape Moses, m…®ne n…ôgkiarien m…®n…ô iran; m…®rap…ôh n…®w…ôs…®kien k…®rik.  
\v 7 M…ôr…®g jiriu r…®rk…ôk meinai Elisabet ror si…ô k…®n ror han…ô, m…®n…ôpiahuaru, k…®ni Sekaraea m…®n r…®n…ôhuaru.   
\p
\v 8 K…®ni ruau…ô atuatuk ye n…®p…®g yame Sekaraea m…®ne kwhen kafan kasor wok kap…ôri…ô ye Nim…ô Ehu…ô kape Kughen.  
\v 9 Kham…ô tuks…ôm-ru m…ô pa nhag…®n tukrauru-p…ôn ye Nim…ô Kape Kughen m…®vaan insens n…ômiov…®n rapien huv…ô mamv…ôn tuk Kughen. K…®ni ye norien kape pris m…®n…ô kape n…®rpenien yermam…ô yame tukr…®v…ôn im…ô, k…®mnharai-p…ôn nhagri…ô ye kwaji kapier k…®rik mhawhan. K…®mnhawhan, kapier yame k…®mnharai-p…ôn nhag Sekaraea iran rukreik…®n hakt…ô.\x - \xo 1:9 \xt Eks 30:7 \x* \fig Pris ravaan …ôru nusai nai ye tebol rhak…ô|alt="Priest burning a sacrifice" src="Hk078b.jpg" size="span" loc="Top of page" copy="Horace Knowles" ref="Luk 1:9" \fig*  
\v 10 M…ôkneik…®n r…®m…ôp…ôh narmam…ô khapsaah iru…ô kasofug…®n mas…ôhuak, k…®ni r…®mauru-p…ôn im…ô m…®vaan insens.   
