\v 27 In m…®v…ôh n…ôgkiarien k…®rik mamv…ôn k…®mi piraov…®n k…®rik nhag…®n e Meri. Yerman r…®p…ôh han…ô n…®v…ônien tukun, m…ôr…®g k…®m…®rpen ta k…®m…ô tuk…®k…®r p…ôn k…®mi kw…ôn k…®rik, nhag…®n e Josef, yame in kw…ôn…ôr…ôus k…®rik kape King Deved.\x - \xo 1:27 \xt Mat 1:16,18 \x*  
