\v 38 M…ôkneik…®n Meri r…®ni-p…ôn tukun m…®m…ô, ‚Äú∆éw…ôh. Yo yorwok …ôm…ô kape Kughen Yermaru. P…ôh In tukror naha nhag…®n k…®mi yo yame ik nakamni.‚Äù K…®ni agelo r…ôta iran, mamv…ôn.   
\s1 Meri r…®mav…ôn m…ôm Elisabet  
