\v 58 K…®ni narmam…ô yam…ô m…®ne kasar…ô ipak…ô tukun m…®ne kafan kw…ôn…ôr…ôus m…®n…ô k…®m…®s…ôr…®g n…ôvsaoyen a m…ô Kughen Yermaru r…®kin rehu…ô tukun mor rhuv…ô p…ôn m…ôknak…®n k…®min, k…®ni iri…ô k…®mnhau…ô m…®sor k…®rikian…ô iri…ô min m…ô tuksagien kwis.   
\p
\v 59 K…®ni n…®p…®g p…®kwarien a r…®m…®v…ôh n…®p…®g eit, k…®ni iri…ô khau…ô mhav…ôh nao k…®m in. K…®ni ipak…ô …ôm…ô k…®shen-p…ôn nhag…®n m…ô n…®fnhag r…®mni e Sekaraea,\x - \xo 1:59 \xt Jen 17:12; Lev 12:3; Luk 2:21 \x*  
\v 60 m…ôr…®g n…®s…®ni r…®m…®ni-p…ôn m…®m…ô, ‚ÄúN…®kam. P…ôh k…®shen-p…ôn nhag…®n m…ô Jon.‚Äù   
\p
\v 61 M…ôr…®g iri…ô khani-p…ôn tukun mham…ô, ‚Äú?Rhawor? Ye kw…ôn…ôr…ôus kap…ômiru, nhag e Jon r…®rk…ôk iran.‚Äù  
\v 62 K…®ni mas…ôgkiar k…®n kwerm…®ri…ô m…®saiyoh-p…ôn Sekaraea mham…ô in rorkeikei m…ô tukshen-p…ôn nhag…®n m…ô pa.   
\p
\v 63 K…®ni in raiyoh-p…ôn …ôri…ô m…ô tukhar…ôh-sip…ôn nar k…®rik p…ôh tukr…®rai-p…ôn n…ôgkiarien k…®rik aik…®n, m…®rai-p…ôn m…®m…ô, ‚ÄúNhag…®n e Jon.‚Äù K…®s…ôm k…®sakur p…®k k…®n. \fig Sekaraia ramni m…ô nhag…®n e Jon|alt="Zecharaia writing down John's name" src="CNT5022.jpg" size="col" loc="Top right" copy="David C. Cook" ref="LUK 1:63" \fig*  
\v 64 M…ôkneik…®n, neram…®n r…®huatuk, m…ôgkiar mamni vi vi Kughen.   
\p
\v 65 K…®ni narmam…ô m-fam yam…ô m…®ne k…®sar…ô ipak…ô tukun k…®sakur k…®n. K…®ni narmam…ô k…®mnhani nar…®mnar m…®n…ô a rarkurao ik…®n m…®n…ô fam ye n…®kar tukwas m…®n…ô ye provins e Judia.  
\v 66 K…®ni narmam…ô m…®fam yam…ô m…®ne k…®mnhav…ôh n…ôvsaoyen a, m…®s…ôt…ôr…®g k…®n, m…®saiyoh …ôri…ô m…®n…ô mham…ô, ‚ÄúMan. ?Keinein m…ô kwajikov…ô e tukreihu…ô mor naha?‚Äù K…®mnhani m…ôknaik…®n meinai k…®m…®s…ôm m…ô n…ôsan…®nien kape Kughen Yermaru ramar…ô iran.   
\s1 Sekaraea r…®m…®ni-…ôrhav n…ôgkiarien yame Kughen r…®m…®v…ôhsi-p…ôn k…®min  
\p
\v 67 M…ôkneik…®n Nanm…®n kape Kughen r…®mnor r…®ki Sekaraea, ramni-…ôrhav n…ôgkiarien yame Kughen r…®m…®v…ôhsi-p…ôn k…®min m…®m…ô,   
\q1
\v 68 ‚ÄúP…ôh khani vi vi Yermaru, In Kughen kape n…ôm…ô Isrel,  
\q2 meinai In r…®mau…ô m…ô tukrasitu ye kafan narmam…ô m…®n…ô,  
\q2 k…®ni m…®p…®k ta …ôri…ô ye kwerm…® t…®km…®r m…®n…ô kap…ôri…ô.\x - \xo 1:68 \xt Sam 72:18 \x*   
\q1
\v 69 In r…®m…®v…ôh-si hakt…ô yem…ô …ôsan…®n yame rav…ôh m…®ragh …ôtaw…ô, yame rams…®-p…ôn ye kw…ôn…ôr…ôus kape yorwok kafan e Deved kup…ôn\x - \xo 1:69 \xt Sam 18:2 \x*  
\v 70 ram…ôri-p…ôn …ôm…ô n…ôgkiarien yame r…®m…®v…ôhsi-p…ôn k…®mi kafan profet kup…ôn m…®n…ô m…®m…ô  
\v 71 tukr…®v…ôhsita …ôtaw…ô tuk t…®km…®r m…®n…ô kap…ôtaw…ô m…®ne tuk kwerm…® narmam…ô m…®fam yam…ô m…®ne kas…ôm…ôk…®n …ôtaw…ô.\x - \xo 1:71 \xt Sam 106:10 \x*   
\q1
\v 72 K…®ni m…®m…ô r…®kin tukreihu…ô tuk r…®ptaw…ô m…®n…ô,  
\q2 k…®ni r…®kin tukram…ôs…®k promes atuatuk\x - \xo 1:72 \xt Jen 17:7; Sam 105:8-9 \x*  
\v 73 yame In r…®m…®ni-p…ôn ta tuk r…®ptaw…ô e Ebraham m…®m…ô\x - \xo 1:73 \xt Jen 22:16-17 \x*  
\v 74 tukr…®r…ôh-si ta …ôtaw…ô ye kwerm…® t…®km…®r m…®n…ô kap…ôtaw…ô,  
\q1 m…ô n…®p…®g m…®fam ye n…®mraghien kap…ôtaw…ô, k…®taw…ô tukharkun n…®sorien wok kafan ye n…®mr…® Kughen, mhap…ôh nhag…®nien,  
\v 75 k…®taw…ô k…®s…ôm…ôrhak…ô m…®satuatuk ye n…®p…®g m…®fam.‚Äù\x - \xo 1:75 \xt Taet 2:12-14 \x*   
\p
\v 76 K…®ni Sekaraea rarar m…®ni-p…ôn tuk t…®ni m…®m…ô,  
\q1 ‚ÄúK…®ni ik, nar…®k, tukokr…ôn k…®n ik k…®m…ô ik pris kape Kughen Yerp…®r…®g;  
\q2 meinai Ik tak…ôkup…ôn k…®n Yermaru mor apn…ôpein…ô ye swatuk kafan,\x - \xo 1:76 \xt Aes 40:3 \x*   
\q1
\v 77 mamni-…ôrhav tuk kafan narmam…ô m…®n…ô m…ô Kughen tukr…ôspir ta t…ôvhag…ô has kap…ôri…ô, m…®v…ôh m…®ragh …ôri…ô.\x - \xo 1:77 \xt Jer 31:34 \x*   
\q1
\v 78 In tukram…ôkeikei mor m…ôknak…®n meinai r…®kin rehu…ô tuk …ôtaw…ô, mamor huv…ô p…ô k…®mi …ôtaw…ô.  
\q1 R…®kin rehu…ô tuk …ôtaw…ô, Kristo tukru…ô tuk …ôtaw…ô r…ômhen …ôm…ô k…®n yame m…®rh ramhakt…ô mamv…ôn ye neai\x - \xo 1:78 \xt Aes 60:1-2 \x*  
\v 79 m…®sia-pen …ôtaw…ô yam…ô m…®ne kasar…ô ye n…ôp…®gnapien m…®ne apa ik…®n n…ôsan…®nien kape n…®mh…ôyen ramhen narmam…ô ik…®n,  
\q2 k…®ni mamk…®r-p…ôn n…®hutaw…ô ye swatuk kape n…ôm…ôrinuyen.‚Äù   
\p
\v 80 K…®ni p…®kwarien a n…®pran ramehu…ô, k…®ni mamehu…ô m…®n ye nanm…®n kape Kughen. K…®ni n…®p…®g m…®fam in ramar…ô apa ye t…®p…ôvs…®k mameito k…®n n…®p…®g atuatuk yame tukr…®rikakun wok iran ye n…®mr…® n…ôm…ô Isrel.   
\c 2  
\s1 Yesu r…®mnarha-p…ô  
\r (Mat 1:18-25)  
\p
\v 1 Ye n…®p…®g a, yem…ô Rom k…®rik, nhag…®n e Sisa Ogastas, in ramarmaru ye tan…ô m…®n…ô fam kape Rom. In mam…ôr…ôhu loa k…®rik m…®m…ô tuk…ôvheik…®n fam narmam…ô yam…ô m…®ne k…®sar…ô aik…®n a.  
\v 2 (In e n…ôvheik…®nien narmam…ô yame k…®mn…ôkup…ôn kor. Ye n…®p…®g a, kw…ôn e Kwaerinias in gavman k…®rik kape provins e Siria).  
\v 3 Kam…ôvheik…®n narmam…ô, narmam…ô tukas…ôkeikei mharer…®g-p…ôn mhav…ôn han…ô im…ôri…ô m…®n…ô ik…®n m…ô tuk…ôvheik…®n …ôri…ô.  
\v 4 Ror p…ôn kw…ôn a Josef m…®n r…®t…ôrhav yerkwanu e Nasaret ye provins e Galili, m…®v…ôn apa provins a Judia, yerkwanu k…®rik kamni k…®m…ô Betlehem, imei King Deved kup…ôn. R…®mav…ôn aik…®n a meinai in kw…ôn…ôr…ôus k…®rik kape King Deved.  
\v 5 Kwerpen ta Josef m…®ne pian e Meri m…ô tukwarkur…ôk; k…®ni Meri natukreim…ôk k…®n kwajikov…ô. K…®ni iriu k…®m…®rav…ôn apa Betlehem m…ô tuk…ôvheik…®n m…®n …ôriu.  
\v 6-7 K…®ni krat…ôrhav Betlehem, m…®rap…ôh n…®w…ômien kw…ônmhan tukwap…®r ik…®n, mwar…ô ye nim…ô kape nar m…®ragh. Mwar…ô han…ô apaik…®n, k…®ni r…®nor n…®p…®g kape kwajikov…ô tukrarha, k…®ni reim…ôk k…®n n…®mr…®n nupan kafan, yerman. Muvr…®g k…®n neip…ôn, m…ôr…ôhu-p…ôn …ôm…ô in ye t…®kirao yame nar m…®ragh m…®n…ô kas…ôv…®g…®n-p…ôn iran.   
\s1 Agelo m…®n…ô khat…ôrhav-p…ô tuk yorwok ye sipsip m…®n…ô  
\p
\v 8 K…®ni ipak…ô …ôm…ô tuk yerkwanu e Betlehem, narmam…ô yam…ô m…®ne kas…ôv…®g…®n sipsip m…®n…ô kasar…ô yerki m…ônvhir…®k masarha tuk sipsip m…®n…ô yenp…®g.  
\v 9 M…ôkneik…®n agelo k…®rik kape Kughen Yermaru r…®t…ôrhav-p…ô tuk …ôri…ô, n…®khakien kape Kughen Yermaru r…®sia-pen …ôri…ô, khag…®n p…®k. \fig Agelo r…®mau…ô m…ôm narmam…ô kasarha tuk sipsip|alt="Angel appears to the shepherds" src="CNT5081.jpg" size="span" loc="Bottom of the page" copy="David C. cook" ref="LUK 2:9" \fig*  
\v 10 M…ôr…®g agelo a r…®m…®ni-p…ôn tuk …ôri…ô m…®m…ô, ‚ÄúHap…ôh nhag…®nien. Meinai yo yakwau…ô m…ô jakni-pre n…ôvsaoyen huv…ô tuk …ômi…ô, yame tukror r…®ki narmam…ô ragien p…®k. K…®ni N…ôvsaoyen a ramv…ôn tuk narmam…ô m…®fam.  
\v 11 Takt…ôkun …ôm…ô, yermam…ô k…®rik r…®mnarha-p…ô ye taon kape King Deved. In rav…ôh m…®ragh narmam…ô, k…®ni In Kristo yame Kughen r…®m…®ni-ta kup…ôn m…ô tukrher-p…ô k…®n tuk …ômi…ô. K…®ni In Yermaru.  
\v 12 K…®ni taks…ôm kwajikov…ô en k…®muvr…®g k…®n neip…ôn, k…ôr…ôhu-p…ôn ye tikirao, ror n…®mt…ôtien k…®mi …ômi…ô m…ô kwajikov…ô a in a yakm…ôni.‚Äù   
\p
\v 13 M…ôkneik…®n, agelo m…®n…ô khapsaah khat…ôrhav-p…ô mas…ôrer iri…ô min, mas…ôgn…ôg…®n Kughen, mhani mham…ô,   
\p
\v 14 ‚ÄúP…ôh khani vi vi Kughen apa yerp…®r…®g ye neai.  
\p K…®ni narmam…ô ye tokrei tan…ô yam…ô m…®ne r…®ki Kughen ramagien tuk …ôri…ô, p…ôh k…®sar…ô ye n…ôm…ôrinuyen.‚Äù\x - \xo 2:14 \xt Luk 19:38 \x*   
\s1 Yorwok ye sipsip m…®n…ô k…®mnhav…ôn mas…ôm Yesu  
\p
\v 15 M…ôkneik…®n agelo m…®n…ô k…®m…®s…ôta ye yorwok ye sipsip m…®n…ô, mharer…®g-p…ôn apa ye rao ye neai, k…®ni yorwok ye sipsip m…®n…ô k…®mnhani tuk …ôri…ô m…®n…ô mham…ô, ‚ÄúP…ôh khav…ôn apa Betlehem, m…®s…ôm-ru nar e Kughen Yermaru r…®m…®ni-p…ô tuk …ôtaw…ô.‚Äù   
\p
\v 16 K…®shai m…®ren mhav…ôn m…®s…ôm Meri m…®ne Josef m…®ne kwajikov…ô yame ramap…®r-p…ôn ye tikirao.  
\v 17 N…®p…®g k…®m…®s…ôm, k…®mnhani …ôrhav n…ôgkiarien yame agelo r…®m…®ni ye kwajikov…ô,  
\v 18 k…®ni narmam…ô m…®fam yam…ô m…®ne k…®m…®s…ôr…®g n…ôgkiarien yame yorwok ye sipsip m…®n…ô k…®mnhani-p…ôn tuk …ôri…ô, k…®sakur p…®k k…®n.  
\v 19 M…ôr…®g Meri r…®mn…ôt…ôr…®g …ôm…ô k…®n nar…®mnar m…®n…ô e, markut tuk n…ôr…®gien n…®pran.\x - \xo 2:19 \xt Luk 2:51 \x*  
\v 20 M…ôr…®g yorwok ye sipsip m…®n…ô k…®mnharer…®g, mhav…ôhsi-hakt…ô nhag Kughen, mhani vi vi In tuk nar…®mnar m-fam yam…ô m…®ne k…®m…®s…ôm m…®s…ôr…®g; r…ômhen …ôm…ô k…®n yame agelo r…®m…®ni-ta tuk …ôri…ô.   
\s1 Kamhen-p…ôn nhag Yesu  
\p
\v 21 Kwajikov…ô a r…®mnarha, m…®v…ôh n…®p…®g eit, k…®ni k…®m…®v…ôh nao k…®min r…ôri-p…ôn …ôm…ô loa kap…ôri…ô, k…®ni khen-p…ôn nhag…®n k…®m…ô Yesu, nhag yame agelo r…®m…®ni-p…ôn ta tuk Meri n…®p…®g in r…®mnor t…®p…®n.\x - \xo 2:21 \xt Luk 1:31 \x*   
\s1 Josef m…®ne Meri k…®m…®r…ôr…ôh Yesu m…®rav…ôn apa ye Nim…ô kape Kughen  
\p
\v 22-24 Ye n…®p…®g a, tukm…ô kwajikov…ô k…®rik rarha, r…®mni m…®ne n…®s…®ni tukaw…ôkeikei mwor sakrefaes kape n…ôspirien mam…ô, r…ôri-p…ôn Loa kape Moses,\f + \fr 2:22-24 \ft  Nak…ôm loa e ye Eks 13:2 m…®ne 1 Saml 1:22-28.\f* k…®ni ruau…ô atuatuk ye n…®p…®g kape Josef m…®ne Meri m…ô tukwor m…ôkna. Ror p…ôn k…®r…ôr…ôh Yesu m…®rhuv…ôn Jerusalem, m…®rav…ôh mak ye tan…ô k…®raru u…ô y…ôkwi-n…ôtu…ôn k…®raru k…®ni mwhopni, r…ôri-p…ôn …ôm…ô loa yame Kughen Yermaru r…®m…®ni.\f + \fr 2:22-24 \ft  Loa e ram…ôm…®r ye Lev 12:8.\f*  
\p K…®ni k…®m…®rav…ôhsi-p…ôn kwajikov…ô a k…®mi Kughen Yermaru. Nar a ram…ôri-p…ôn N…ôgkiarien kape Kughen yame ramni m…®m…ô,  
\q1 ‚ÄúN…®mr…®n nupan m…®n…ô yerman, tukam…ôkeikei k…®v…ôhsi-p…ôn …ôri…ô k…®mi Kughen Yermaru m…ô kafan m…®n…ô.‚Äù\rq (Eks 13:2, 12)\rq*   
\s1 Simeon m…®ne Ana k…®maw…ôm Yesu, kaw…ôgn…ôg…®n Kughen  
\p
\v 25 K…®ni huaru k…®rik ramar…ô apa Jerusalem, nhag…®n e Simeon. Kafan n…®mraghien in ratuatuk huv…ô, k…®ni n…®p…®g m…®fam in ram…ôri-p…ôn n…ôgkiarien kape Kughen. K…®ni in rameito k…®n nu…ôyen kape Kristo yame In tukru…ô m…®v…ôh m…®ragh n…ôm…ô Isrel. K…®ni Nanm…®n kape Kughen ru…ô m…®kuar yerkin.  
\v 26 Nanm…®n kape Kughen ru…®ni-p…ôn ta tukun m…®m…ô tukr…®p…ôh n…®mh…ôyen meriaji tukr…ôm Kristo yame Kughen Yermaru r…®m…®ni m…ô tukrher-p…ô k…®n.  
\v 27 K…®ni Nanm…®n kape Kughen r…®mnor r…®kin m…ô tukrauru-p…ôn ye Nim…ô Ehu…ô kape Kughen. K…®ni Josef m…®ne Meri k…®m…®r…ôr…ôh Yesu mwaru-p…ôn ye Nim…ô kape Kughen m…ô iriu tukwor nar…®mnar fam yame Loa kape Moses ramni.  
\v 28 M…ôkneik…®n Simeon r…®mn…ôm Yesu, k…®ni m…®r…ôh k…®n kwerm…®n, k…®ni mamni vi vi Kughen mamni-p…ôn tukun m…®m…ô,   
\q1
\v 29 ‚ÄúKughen Yermaru, promes yame Ik n…®m…®ni tuk yo, naknor …ôfrak…®s.  
\q2 K…®ni takt…ôkun ai, eighaan k…®n yo, yorwok e kafam, p…ôh yakmh…ô ye n…ôm…ôrinuyen,   
\q1
\v 30 meinai yakn…ôm kwajikov…ô e k…®n n…®mr…®k yame tukr…®w…ôh m…®ragh narmam…ô.\x - \xo 2:30 \xt Aes 52:10; Luk 3:6; Taet 2:11 \x*   
\q1
\v 31 Ik n…®mnor apn…ôpein…ô m…ô In tukr…®v…ôh m…®ragh narmam…ô,  
\q2 k…®ni narmam…ô m-fam tukharkun nar a.   
\q1
\v 32 In tukru…ô r…ômhen k…®n laet, mhajoun swatuk k…®n n…ôm…ô ye kantri p…®s…®n p…®s…®n m…®n…ô,  
\q2 K…®ni narmam…ô tukhav…ôhsi-hakt…ô n…ôm…ô Isrel tukun.‚Äù\x - \xo 2:32 \xt Aes 42:6; 49:6; 52:10 \x*   
\p
\v 33 K…®ni r…®m kwajikov…ô a m…®ne n…®s…®ni kwakur p…®k k…®n n…ôgkiarien yame Simeon r…®m…®ni iran.  
\v 34 K…®ni Simeon r…ôhuak m…®m…ô, ‚ÄúP…ôh n…®huv…ôyen kape Kughen tukrur…ô tuk …ômiru.‚Äù K…®ni m…®ni-p…ôn tuk Meri, n…®s…®n kwajikov…ô a, m…®m…ô,  
\p ‚Äú!∆ér…®g-ru! Kughen r…®m…®rpen ta kwajikov…ô e m…ô tukror n…ôm…ô Isrel khapsaah tukham…®r,  
\q2 k…®ni m…ô tukror m…®n …ôri…ô khapsaah khav…ôh n…®mraghien.  
\q1 Kughen r…®m…®rpen pawk In m…ô In ror n…®mt…ôtien k…®rik, m…ôr…®g narmam…ô tukhani hah In.\x - \xo 2:34 \xt Aes 8:14; Mat 21:42; 1 Pita 2:8\x*  
\v 35 Ror p…ôn tuk…ôm …ôpu n…ôr…®gien has kape narmam…ô khapsaah.  
\q1 K…®ni, Meri, r…®kim tukr…ômh…ô tukun r…ômhen k…®n yame yermam…ô k…®rik ramhai r…®kim k…®n nau nis…ô.‚Äù   
\p
\v 36 K…®ni piahwaru k…®rik ramar…ô aik…®n, nhag…®n e Ana. In profet k…®rik. In ji Fanuel, kw…ôn…ôr…ôus kape Aser kup…ôn. R…®n…ôpiahuaru …ôgk…ôp. N…®p…®g r…®mnam…ôtamaru…ô …ôm…ô, m…ôri-p…ôn kafan yerman. Mwar…ô kwis kape newk seven …ôm…ô, kw…ôn a r…®mh…ô.  
\v 37 R…®mnar…ô p…®s…®n …ôm…ô m…ôknak…®n meriaji m…®pi…ôhuaru. K…®ni takt…ôkun ai kafan newk eiti fo. N…®p…®g m…®fam in ram…ôm…®r ye Nim…ô kape Ehu…ô Kughen mam…ôhuak, yenp…®g m…®ne yeraan. Matuak…ôm m…®p…ôh n…ôv…®g…®nien m…ô tukr…ôhuak k…®mi Kughen.  
\v 38 K…®ni in r…®mau…ô atuatuk ye n…®p…®g yame Simeon ram…ôgkiar k…®n kwajikov…ô a. K…®ni piahwaru ai r…®m…®ni vi vi Kughen tukun, k…®ni mam…ôgkiar ye kwajikov…ô e k…®mi narmam…ô m…®fam yam…ô m…®ne kamhawhin m…ô Kristo tukr…®r…®s…®n n…ôm…ô Jerusalem.   
\s1 Josef m…®ne Meri k…®m…®rav…ôn apa Nasaret  
\p
\v 39 K…®ni Josef m…®ne Meri k…®m…®wor nar…®mnar fam yame Loa kape Kughen Yermaru ramni, k…®ni m…ôrh…®rer…®g-p…ôn im…ôris…®r ik…®n Nasaret ye provins e Galili.\x - \xo 2:39 \xt Mat 2:23 \x*  
\v 40 Kwajikov…ô a r…®nehu…ô mu…®skai, mu…®rkun huv…ô nar, k…®ni n…®p…®g m-fam n…®huv…ôyen kape Kughen rukwar ye kafan n…®mraghien.   
\s1 Tamaru…ô e Yesu ramv…ôn apa Nim…ô Ehu…ô kape Kughen  
\p
\v 41 Ye newk m…®n…ô fam, r…®m Yesu m…®ne n…®s…®ni k…®m…®rav…ôn apa Jerusalem m…ô tukwor lafet kape Pasova.\f + \fr 2:41 \ft  Ye n…®p…®g kape lafet kape N…ôvi…ôrok…®nien, u…ô Pasova, n…ôm…ô Isrel r…®kiri…ô ram…ôs…®k Kughen r…®m…®w…ôh m…®ragh kw…ôn…ôr…ôus kup…ôn kap…ôri…ô m…®r…ôh-si ta …ôri…ô ye kwerm…® yamehu…ô kape Ijip. ∆ém-ru stori kape Pasova ye Eksodas 12:21-27.\f*  
\v 42 K…®ni n…®p…®g Yesu r…®m…®v…ôh newk twelef, k…®m…®wor norien yame kawor han…ô, k…®ni Yesu r…®kwas…®g k…®n …ôriu m…®rh…®v…ôn apa fakt…ô ye lafet a.  
\v 43 K…®ni lafet r…®nor infamien, k…®ni kafan m…®n…ô k…®mnharer…®g mhav…ôn im…ôri…ô ik…®n; m…ôr…®g tamaru…ô Yesu In r…®p…ôh n…®kwas…®gien k…®n r…®mni m…®ne n…®s…®ni, mam…ôm…®r …ôm…ô apa Jerusalem. K…®ni iriu kweinein.  
\v 44 Kr…ôm…ô-ta m…ô ramkwas…®g k…®n …ôri…ô. K…®ni k…®m…®s…ôriw…ôk mamhav…ôn tuk n…®p…®g pi…ôpi…ô k…®rik. M…®pir…ôrikakun mwarha-k…®n yerki kw…ôn…ôr…ôus kap…ôriu m…®ne iriu m…®n…ô t…®ks…®n.  
\v 45 M…ôr…®g k…®rap…ôh n…®w…ômien In, mwarha-k…®n, m…®rarer…®g m…®rav…ôn Jerusalem.  
\v 46 Kwarha-k…®n In n…®p…®g k…®sis…ôr, k…®ni m…®piw…ôm apa ye Nim…ô Ehu…ô kape Kughen. Ramkw…ôt…ô iri…ô n…ômhajoun m…®n…ô, mam…ôt…ôr…®g k…®n …ôri…ô. K…®ni mamaiyoh …ôri…ô k…®n nar…®mnar t…®ks…®n.  
\v 47 K…®ni narmam…ô m…®fam k…®m…®s…ôr…®g In, k…®sakur tuk kafan n…®rkunien m…®ne nhorp…®nien n…ôgkiarien m…®n…ô kafan.  
\v 48 K…®ni r…®mni m…®ne n…®s…®ni k…®m…®w…ôm In, kwakur p…®k k…®n. K…®ni n…®s…®ni r…®m…®ni-p…ôn tukun m…®m…ô, ‚ÄúNar…®k. ?N…®mnhawor mor m…ôkneik…®n ir…ômru? !∆ér…®g-ru! !K…®mru r…®m…®m, r…®kimru r…ômh…ô p…®k tuk ik, k…®ni yakwarha-k…®n p…®k ik!‚Äù   
\p
\v 49 M…ôr…®g In r…®ni-p…ôn tuk …ôriu m…®m…ô, ‚Äú?Nakawarha-k…®n Yo tuk naha? Tukm…ô ror nakrap…ôh n…®rarkunien m…ô Yo jakam…ôkeikei mam…ôm…®r ye Nim…ô kape R…®m…®k.‚Äù  
\v 50 M…ôr…®g iriu k…®r…ôp…ôh n…®rarkunien n…®prai n…ôgkiarien yame r…®m…®ni-p…ôn tuk …ôriu.   
\p
\v 51 K…®ni In r…®kwas…®g k…®n …ôriu, m…®rheiwaiyu m…®rh…®v…ôn apa Nasaret. K…®ni In r…®m…®siai …ôriu mamor n…ôkwairiu. M…ôr…®g n…®p…®g m…®fam n…®s…®ni ram…ôt…ôr…®g k…®n nar…®mnar m…®n…ô fam a.\x - \xo 2:51 \xt Luk 2:19 \x*  
\v 52 K…®ni Yesu n…®pran ramehu…ô, k…®ni kafan n…®rkunien ramhakt…ô p…®k. K…®ni ye n…®p…®g m…®fam, Kughen m…®ne narmam…ô, r…®kiri…ô ragien …ôm…ô tukun.\x - \xo 2:52 \xt 1 Saml 2:26; Prov 3:4 \x*   
\c 3  
\s1 Jon Baptaes ram…ôvsao-…ôrhav k…®n n…ôgkiarien kape Kughen  
\r (Mat 3:1-12; Mak 1:1-8; Jon 1:19-28)  
\p
\v 1 Kwas…®g ik…®n ye nar…®mnar m…®n…ô a, yem…ô Rom k…®rik, nhag…®n e Taebirias Sisa, in ramehu…ô ye provins m…®n…ô fam kape Rom. K…®ni ye n…®p…®g in r…®namarmaru meriaji newk fiftin, k…®ni kwerm…®n m…®n…ô t…®ks…®n e: Herod Antipas ramehu…ô ye provins e Galili; m…®ne piauni Filip in ramehu…ô ye provins mir e Ituria m…®ne Trakonaetas, m…®ne Lisanias ramehu…ô ye provins e Abilin, m…®ne Ponjes Paelat in gavman kape provins e Judia.  
\v 2 In e ye n…®p…®g atuatuk kape Anas m…®ne Kaefas yame iriu jif pris mir.  
\p Ye n…®p…®g a, Jon, ji Sekaraea, yame r…®nehu…ô ta ai, mamar…ô apa ik…®n ruhiko ik…®n, k…®ni Kughen r…®m…®v…ôh-sip…ôn n…ôgkiarien k…®rik k…®min.  
\v 3 K…®ni in r…®mnokr…ôn apomh p…ôn ik…®n m…®n…ô ipak…ô tuk nu apa Jodan mam…ôvsao-…ôrhav k…®n n…ôgkiarien kape Kughen. In mamni-p…ôn m…®m…ô narmam…ô tukas…ôkeikei m…®sarar ye n…ôr…®gien kap…ôri…ô tuk t…ôvhag…ô has, k…®ni mhav…ôn tuk Kughen m…ô In tukr…ôspir norien has m…®n…ô kap…ôri…ô. K…®ni m…ô n…®mt…ôtien k…®rik e, tukor baptaes ir…ôri…ô.\x - \xo 3:3 \xt Wok 13:24 \x*  
\v 4 In r…ôri-p…ôn …ôm…ô n…ôgkiarien yame Aesea r…®m…®rai kup…ôn ye n…ôkw…ôkw…ô kafan m…®m…ô,  
\q1 ‚ÄúKw…ôn k…®rik ramokr…ôn ehu…ô apa ik…®n ruhiko ik…®n mamni m…®m…ô,  
\q1 ‚ÄòK…®mi…ô taksor apn…ôpein…ô ye swatuk kape Yermaru,  
\q2 k…®ni m…®sor kafan swatuk ratuatuk.   
\q1
\v 5 N…®kw…ôtan…ô m…®n…ô fam tuksuun huv…ô,  
\q2 k…®ni tukwas m…®n…ô m…®ne nahawk m…®n…ô fam tuks…ôt…ôn-…ôt…ôn,  
\q1 k…®ni swatuk iko iko m…®n…ô tuk…ôr…ôhu atuatuk,  
\q2 k…®ni swatuk yame rap…ôjiap…ôt tuk…ôkeikei kor r…®pi…ô.   
\q1
\v 6 K…®ni narmam…ô m…®fam tuks…ôm swatuk kape Kughen tuk n…®v…ôh-m…®raghien narmam…ô.‚Äô‚Äù\rq (Aes 40:3-5)\rq*   
\p
\v 7 K…®ni ye n…®p…®g a, narmam…ô khapsaah k…®mnhav…ôn tuk Jon m…ô in tukror baptaes ir…ôri…ô; m…ôr…®g r…®ni-p…ôn tuk …ôri…ô m…®m…ô, ‚Äú!K…®mi…ô naksahas r…ômhen …ôm…ô k…®n snek yam…ô m…®ne kas…ôrhkwopah! P…ôh nien m…ô tuktu, Kughen ror niemhaa m…®v…ôhsi-p…ôn narp…®nien k…®mi narmam…ô. ?M…ôr…®g, pa ramni m…ô to k…®mi…ô nakharkun n…®saptayen k…®n?\x - \xo 3:7 \xt Mat 12:34; 23:33 \x*  
\v 8 Sor nar…®mnar t…®ks…®n yam…ô rhuv…ô m…ô tuks…ôm m…ô nakw…ôs…ôp…ôh …ôfrak…®s norien has m…®n…ô k…®ni mhav…ôn tuk Kughen. N…ôfrak…®sien m…ô k…®mi…ô kw…ôn…ôr…ôus kape Ebraham, m…ôr…®g r…®kimi…ô tukr…®p…ôh n…ôs…®kien m…ô Kughen tukram…ôkeikei m…®v…ôh m…®ragh …ômi…ô mhawor k…®mi…ô kw…ôn…ôr…ôus kape Ebraham. !N…®kam, in nar apnap…®g …ôm…ô! Yakamni-pre tuk …ômi…ô m…ô Kughen r…®rkun nor-m…®n-ien kapier apnap…®g ru…ô r…ômhen k…®n kw…ôn…ôr…ôus kape Ebraham.\x - \xo 3:8 \xt Jon 8:33,39 \x*  
\v 9 K…®ni takt…ôkun ai, Kughen r…®n…ôrer matuk ta m…ô tukr…ôr…ôru nuknei nai. K…®ni tukm…ô nai k…®rik r…®p…ôh n…®ku…ôyen k…®n kw…ônkwan yame rhuv…ô, k…®ni tukr…ôr…ôru marakik…®n-p…ôn ye nap.‚Äù\f + \fr 3:9 \ft  Jon Baptaes ram…ôgkiar skai k…®mi Farisi m…®ne Sadusi, yam…ô m…®ne kham…ô ta m…ô Kughen tukram…ôkeikei m…®v…ôh m…®ragh …ôri…ô meinai iri…ô ji Ebraham m…®n…ô. Nuhp…®k…®nien ye nai yame Kughen tukr…ôr…ôru ramhajoun m…ô Kughen tukr…ôkir norien kape narmam…ô, k…®ni yam…ô m…®ne khap…ôh n…®sorien norien huv…ô, Kughen tukr…®v…ôh-si-p…ôn narp…®nien k…®mi …ôri…ô.\f*\x - \xo 3:9 \xt Mat 7:19 \x*   
\p
\v 10 K…®ni kwhen ehu…ô a k…®m…®saiyoh Jon mham…ô, ‚Äú?M…ôr…®g, naha nhag…®n k…®maw…ô jakas…ôkeikei m…®sor?‚Äù   
\p
\v 11 K…®ni Jon r…®ni-p…ôn tuk …ôri…ô m…®m…ô, ‚ÄúTukm…ô kafam neip…ôn k…®raru, v…ôhsi-p…ôn k…®rik k…®mi yermam…ô yame kafan r…®rk…ôk. K…®ni tukm…ô nam n…ôv…®g…®nien rar…ô, …ôhi-p…ôn t…®ks…®n k…®mi narmam…ô yam…ô m…®ne n…ôri…ô r…®rk…ôk.‚Äù   
\p
\v 12 K…®ni narmam…ô t…®ks…®n yam…ô m…®ne kas…ôrer tuk mane kape takis k…®mnhau…ô m…ô Jon tukor baptaes ir…ôri…ô, k…®n m…®saiyoh in mham…ô, ‚Äú?Naha e nhag…®n k…®maw…ô jakas…ôkeikei m…®sor?‚Äù\x - \xo 3:12 \xt Luk 7:29 \x*   
\p
\v 13 K…®ni Jon r…®ni-p…ôn tuk …ôri…ô m…®m…ô, ‚ÄúTakhap…ôh nhav…ôh-sitayen mane tuk narmam…ô rapita yame r…ômhen m…ô takhav…ôh.‚Äù   
\p
\v 14 K…®ni mobael m…®n…ô t…®ks…®n k…®m…®saiyoh m…®n mham…ô, ‚Äú?M…ôr…®g rhawor ir…ômaw…ô? ?Naha e nhag…®n k…®maw…ô jakas…ôkeikei m…®sor?‚Äù  
\p K…®ni in r…®ni-p…ôn tuk …ôri…ô m…®m…ô, ‚ÄúTakhap…ôh nhaviyen n…®g…®nien k…®mi narmam…ô mham…ô, ‚ÄòTukm…ô nakhap…ôh nhav…ôh-si-p…ôyen mane, k…®ni jaksor n…ômh…ôyen k…®mi …ômi…ô, u…ô jaksor …ômi…ô naksarer ye n…®mr…® m…®rh k…®ni yakhani hah …ômi…ô.‚Äô M…ôr…®g r…®kimi…ô tukram…ôkeikei mamagien …ôm…ô tuk n…ôrok atuatuk kap…ômi…ô.‚Äù   
\p
\v 15 K…®ni narmam…ô m…®n…ô a kas…ôm m…®s…ôm, r…®kiri…ô ruh m…ô tukm…ô ror Jon in Kristo yame Kughen r…®m…®ni m…ô tukrher-p…ô k…®n.  
\v 16 M…ôr…®g Jon rhorp…®n n…ôt…ôr…®gien kap…ôri…ô m…®m…ô, ‚ÄúYo yakamor baptaes ir…ômi…ô k…®n nu, m…ôr…®g yermam…ô k…®rik tukr…®piu…ô yame kafan n…ôsan…®nien m…®ne nehu…ôyen rapita yo. K…®ni yo ye tan…ô …ôgk…ôp; yakp…ôh n…ômhenien m…ô to yak…ôn…®mkur m…®r…®s…®n ta n…ôr…ôus ye kafan sandel. K…®ni In tukror baptaes ir…ômi…ô ye Nanm…®n kape Kughen m…®ne nap.\x - \xo 3:16 \xt Wok 13:25 \x*  
\v 17 In ram…ôrer matuk tuk n…ômien norien kape narmam…ô mam…ôwhai …ôri…ô, n…ôm…ô huv…ô m…®n…ô m…®ne n…ôm…ô has m…®n…ô. R…ômhen …ôm…ô k…®n yame yem…ôsim rav…ôh safel tuk n…ôspir-tayen t…®ki kw…ônkwai wit m…ô tukr…®p…®k n…®mit…®n yame rhuv…ô. Narmam…ô yam…ô m…®ne khahuv…ô k…®s…ômhen k…®n n…®mit wit, r…®p…®k …ôri…ô mamv…ôn yerkwanu. M…ôr…®g narmam…ô has k…®s…ômhen k…®n t…®ki kw…ônkwai wit, ramarakik…®n-p…ôn …ôri…ô ye nap ehu…ô yame ramu…ôk rer…®n.‚Äù   
\p
\v 18 K…®ni Jon ramni-…ôrhav n…ôgkiarien r…®psaah mamor kwir…®g k…®n k…®mi narmam…ô m…ô tukr…®vi-p…ô n…ôt…ôr…®gien kape narmam…ô khau…ô tuk Kughen.   
\s1 Herod r…®m…®v…ôh-sip…ôn Jon Baptaes ye kalabus  
\r (Mak 6:14-29)  
\p
\v 19 Ye n…®p…®g a, Herod Antipas r…®m…®k…®r ta Herodias in e piahwaru kape piauni, k…®ni mamor nar…®mnar r…®psaah yame rahas. M…ôr…®g Jon rokr…ôn skai k…®min tukun.\x - \xo 3:19 \xt Mat 14:3-4; Mak 6:17-18 \x*  
\v 20 Ror p…ôn Herod r…®mn…ôs…®k …ôpnis p…ôn m…®n ye norien has kafan m…®v…ôhsi-p…ôn Jon ye kalabus.   
\s1 Jon r…®mnor baptaes ye Yesu  
\r (Mat 3:13-17; Mak 1:9-11)  
\p
\v 21 M…ôr…®g kwas…®g ik…®n Jon r…®v…ôn ye kalabus, k…®ni in r…®namor baptaes ye narmam…ô, k…®ni Yesu m…®n r…®mav…ôn, Jon ror baptaes iran. K…®ni n…®p…®g Yesu r…®mnam…ôhuak, Kughen r…®mn…ôhit…ô ye neai,  
\v 22 k…®ni Nanm…®n kape Kughen r…®s…®-fakt…ô meiwaiyu iran, n…®pran r…ômhen k…®n mak ye tan…ô, k…®ni n…ôgkiarien k…®rik r…®s…®-p…ôn ye rao ye neai mamni m…®m…ô, ‚ÄúIk nar…®k keikei; r…®kik ragien p…®k tuk ik.‚Äù\x - \xo 3:22 \xt Jon 1:32 \x*   
\s1 R…®p Yesu m…®n…ô  
\p
\v 23 N…®p…®g Yesu r…®m…®rikakun kafan wok, kafan newk r…ômhen k…®n toti. Narmam…ô kham…ô ta m…ô in ji Josef.  
