\c 4  
\s1 Setan r…®m…®v…ôhsi-p…ôn w…ôhsi-p…ôn k…®mi Yesu  
\r (Mat 4:1-11; Mak 1:12-13)  
\p
\v 1 Nanm…®n kape Kughen r…®m…®kuar ye n…®mraghien kape Yesu, k…®ni ye n…®p…®g ruas…®-p…ôn ye nu apa Jodan, Nanm…®n kape Kughen r…®k…®r In m…®v…ôn apa ik…®n ruhiko ik…®n.  
\v 2 Aik…®n, Setan ramarkut m…ô tukrukrao ye n…ôr…®gien kafan kape n…®p…®g foti. Ye n…®p…®g m…®n…ô fam a, In rap…ôh n…ôv…®g…®nien, k…®ni ye n…®p…®g infamien, n…®kumh…ô r…ôs p…®k.  
\v 3 K…®ni Setan r…®ni-p…ôn tukun m…®m…ô, ‚ÄúTukm…ô ik Ji Kughen …ôfrah, ni-p…ôn tuk kapier e m…ô rukreik…®n mu…ô mor bred k…®n.‚Äù  
\v 4 M…ôr…®g Yesu rhorp…®n m…®m…ô, ‚ÄúK…®m…®rai ye N…ôkw…ôkw…ô kape Kughen k…®m…ô, ‚ÄòYermam…ô r…®p…ôh n…®mraghien …ôm…ô ye n…ôv…®g…®nien.‚Äô\rq ( Dut 8:3)\rq*‚Äù   
\p
\v 5 M…ôkneik…®n Setan r…®k…®r Yesu m…®v…ôn apa ye tukwas apomh k…®rik, k…®ni takt…ôkun …ôm…ô, rhajoun In k…®n kantri m…®n…ô fam ye tokrei tan…ô,  
\v 6 k…®ni m…®ni-p…ôn tukun m…®m…ô, ‚ÄúYo jak…ôr…ôhu-pre narmaruyen ye tan…®mtan…ô ye kwerm…®m, m…®ne naut…ô kap…ôri…ô m…®n…ô fam, meinai nar…®mnar m…®fam a ram…ôm…®r ye kwerm…®k, k…®ni yak…®rkun neighan-p…ônien k…®n k…®mi naha yermam…ô yame yakorkeikei m…ô jakv…ôhsi-p…ôn k…®min.  
\v 7 K…®ni tukm…ô nak…ôhuak k…®mi yo, nar…®mnar m-fam ai ik takor kafam k…®n.‚Äù   
\p
\v 8 M…ôr…®g Yesu rhorp…®n kafan n…ôgkiarien m…®m…ô, ‚ÄúN…ôkw…ôkw…ô kape Kughen ramni m…®m…ô, ‚ÄòTaks…ôhuak …ôm…ô k…®mi kap…ômi…ô Yermaru Kughen, m…®s…ôri-p…ôn …ôm…ô kafan n…ôr…®gien.‚Äô\rq (Dut 6:13)\rq*‚Äù   
\p
\v 9 M…ôkneik…®n Setan r…®k…®r In m…ôr…®p In apa Jerusalem mhakt…ô ye tokrei Nim…ô Ehu…ô kape Kughen apa yerp…®r…®g …ôgk…ôp. K…®ni m…®ni-p…ôn tukun m…®m…ô, ‚ÄúTukm…ô ik Ji Kughen …ôfrak…®s, iv-…ôrhav-ru ik…®n e,  
\v 10 meinai k…®m…®rai k…®m…ô,  
\q1 ‚Äú‚ÄòIn tukrher-p…ô k…®n agelo m…®n…ô kafan khau…ô masarha huv…ô tuk ik.   
\q2
\v 11 Tukharapt…ôr…ôk…®n ik k…®n kwerm…®ri…ô m…ô takp…ôh nowhan-p…ônien n…®hum ye kapier k…®rik.‚Äô‚Äù\rq (Sam 91:11, 12)\rq*   
\p
\v 12 M…ôr…®g Yesu rhorp…®n kafan n…ôgkiarien m…®m…ô, ‚ÄúM…ôr…®g N…ôkw…ôkw…ô kape Kughen ramni m…®m…ô, ‚ÄúTakhap…ôh n…®s…ôm-…ôsaahyen kap…ômi…ô Kughen Yermaru m…ô ramarha huv…ô …ôfrak…®s tuk …ômi…ô u…ô n…®kam.‚Äô\rq (Dut 6:16)\rq* ‚Äù   
\p
\v 13 K…®ni Setan ror infamien ye n…®v…ôhsi-p…ôn v…ôhsi-p…ônien k…®mi Yesu; m…ôkneik…®n, mapitan k…®n Yesu mawhin n…®p…®g huv…ô yame tukru…ô m…®n tukun.\x - \xo 4:13 \xt Hib 2:18; 4:15 \x*   
\s1 Yesu r…®m…®rikakun kafan wok  
\r (Mat 4:12-17; Mak 1:14-15)  
\p
\v 14 K…®ni ai, Yesu r…®m…®rer…®g-p…ôn Galili, k…®ni n…ôsan…®nien kape Nanm…®n kape Kughen r…®m…®kuar ye n…®mraghien kafan. K…®ni k…®mn…ôvsao k…®n In rarkurao ye tan…ô a.  
\v 15 K…®ni Yesu r…®mnhajoun ye nim…ô kape nofug…®nien m…®n…ô, k…®ni narmam…ô m-fam khani vi vi In.   
\s1 N…ôm…ô ime Yesu k…®m…®s…ôp…ôh In  
\p
\v 16 K…®ni Yesu r…®mau…ô Nasaret, aik…®n r…®mnehu…ô ik…®n kup…ôn. K…®ni ye Sabat k…®rik, In r…®mav…ôn ye nim…ô kape nofug…®nien r…ômhen …ôm…ô k…®n yame ramor han…ô. K…®ni m…ôrer m…ô tukr…ôvheik…®n N…ôkw…ôkw…ô kape Kughen, \fig N…ôkw…ôkw…ô kape profet, yame k…®mnarp…ôv…®n-arp…ôv…®n|alt="Prophets words written on a scroll" src="HK071A.jpg" size="col" loc="Near to the text" copy="Horace Knowles" ref="LUK 4:16" \fig*  
\v 17 k…®ni k…®v…ôhsi-p…ôn n…ôkw…ôkw…ô yame k…®mnarp…ôv…®n-arp…ôv…®n yame profet Aesaea r…®m…®rai kup…ôn. K…®ni ruhatuk…®n n…ôkw…ôkw…ô m…ôm n…ôgkiarien yame Aesaea r…®m…®rai yame ramni m…®m…ô,   
\q1
\v 18 ‚ÄúNanm…®n kape Kughen ramar…ô irak  
\q2 meinai In r…®m…®rpen yo,  
\q2 jak…ôvsao-…ôrhav k…®n n…ôgkiarien huv…ô k…®mi yav…ôn hah m…®n…ô.  
\q1 K…®ni In rher-p…ô k…®n yo m…ô jakv…ôn mamni-p…ôn tuk narmam…ô yam…ô m…®ne k…®v…ôhsi-p…ôn …ôri…ô ye kalabus m…ô tuk…®r…®s…®n …ôri…ô,  
\q2 k…®ni m…®ni-p…ôn tuk n…®mr…®n p…®s m…®n…ô m…ô tuks…ôm m…®n nar.  
\q1 K…®ni rher-p…ô k…®n yo m…ô jakr…®s…®n narmam…ô yam…ô m…®ne kas…ôm…®r ye kwerm…® narmam…ô p…®s…®n mas…ôr…®g rahah,   
\q1
\v 19 mamni-…ôrhav m…ô n…®p…®g ruau…ô ta yame Kughen Yermaru tukrhajoun kafan n…®huv…ôyen m…®v…ôh m…®ragh narmam…ô.‚Äù\rq (Aes 61:1, 2)\rq*   
\p
\v 20 Yesu r…®mn…ôhueik…®n ta n…ôkw…ôkw…ô a, k…®ni meiwaiyu m…®v…ôhsi-p…ôn m…®n k…®mi yermam…ô yame ramarha huv…ô tuk n…ôkw…ôkw…ô m…®n…ô, k…®ni mamkw…ôt…ô m…ô tukr…ôvhag k…®mi narmam…ô. K…®ni narmam…ô m-fam ye nim…ô kape nofug…®nien kasarha t…®m t…®m iran.  
\v 21 K…®ni In ram…ôgkiar k…®mi …ôri…ô mamni m…®n m…®m…ô, ‚ÄúTakt…ôkun ai, ye n…®p…®g yame n…®m…®s…ôr…®g N…ôkw…ôkw…ô e Kape Kughen, n…®niyen a ruau…ô m…®nor n…ôfrak…®sien k…®n.‚Äù   
\p
\v 22 K…®ni narmam…ô m…®fam kas…ôgn…ôg…®n In, k…®ni k…®sakur p…®k tuk n…ôgkiarien huv…ô yam…ô m…®ne ramni, k…®ni m…®saiyoh …ôri…ô m…®n…ô mham…ô, ‚Äú?M…ôr…®g kw…ôn e In ji Josef …ôm…ô u…ô?‚Äù\x - \xo 4:22 \xt Luk 3:23; Jon 6:42 \x*   
\p
\v 23 K…®ni Yesu r…®ni-p…ôn tuk …ôri…ô m…®m…ô, ‚ÄúYak…®rkun m…ô takpihani n…ôgkiarien akwas e tuk yo yame ramni m…®m…ô, ‚ÄòDokta, or huv…ô atuk-ru n…®pram,‚Äô mhani m…®n mham…ô, ‚ÄòNar…®mnar yam…ô m…®ne y…®m…®s…ôr…®g m…ô n…®mnor ta apa Kapaneam, rhuv…ô m…ô taku…ô mor m…®n e, imam ik…®n.‚Äô  
\v 24 N…ôfrak…®sien, yakamni tuk …ômi…ô m…ô narmam…ô to khap…ôh nhasiaiyen profet k…®rik yame rams…®-p…ôn ir…ôri…ô.\x - \xo 4:24 \xt Jon 4:44 \x*  
\v 25 Ye n…®p…®g kape Elaeja, n…ôhig r…®p…ôh n…®pien newk k…®sis…ôr m…®ne maku…ô sikis, k…®ni n…®kumh…ô rav…ôn ik…®n m…®n…ô fam, n…ôv…®g…®nien r…®rk…ôk. K…®ni yakni n…ôfrak…®sien tuk …ômi…ô m…®m…ô, ye n…®p…®g a n…®piahuaru k…®mh…ô tan k…®n …ôri…ô khapsaah e Isrel,\x - \xo 4:25 \xt 1 King 17:1,7 \x*  
\v 26 m…ôr…®g p…ôh nien m…ô Kughen rher-p…ô k…®n Elaeja m…ô tukr…®v…ôn masitu ir…ôri…ô. N…®kam. In rher-p…ô k…®n m…ô tukrasitu …ôm…ô ye piahwaru k…®rik yerkwanu Jarefat apa ye provins e Saedon. M…ôr…®g piahwaru a p…ôh nien m…ô pian Isrel.\x - \xo 4:26 \xt 1 King 17:8-16 \x*  
\v 27 K…®ni ye n…®p…®g kape profet e Elisa, narmam…ô khapsaah k…®mn…®sar…ô Isrel yam…ô m…®ne kamhaw…ôh n…ômh…ôyen e ‚Äòleprosi‚Äô\f + \fr 4:27 \ft  Leprosi in n…ômh…ôyen skai k…®rik yame ram…ôm…®r ye t…®ki yermam…ô.\f* m…ôr…®g Elisa r…®p…ôh nor-huv…ôyen k…®rik. M…ôr…®g in r…®mnor huv…ô …ôm…ô kw…ôn Siria e Neman, yame p…ôh nien m…ô yem…ô Isrel.‚Äù\x - \xo 4:27 \xt 2 King 5:1-14 \x*   
\p
\v 28 Narmam…ô ye nim…ô kape nofug…®nien k…®m…®s…ôr…®g n…ôgkiarien a, niemhaa rhai p…®k …ôri…ô m-fam.  
\v 29 K…®ni k…®sarar mhar…ôh In, m…®s…ôuk…ôkin mhat…ôrhav yerkwanu, mhav…ôn m…®sokrig ye tukwas yame k…®mnor taon ik…®n, m…ô tuksarkw…ôrhav k…®n apa ik…ôut…ôn.  
\v 30 M…ôr…®g Yesu r…®v…ôn-p…ôn ta ye kw…ôn…®mrheri…ô, map.   
\s1 Yesu r…®mn…ôko ta yarmh…ô ye yermam…ô k…®rik  
\r (Mak 1:21-28)  
\p
\v 31 K…®ni Yesu r…®mneiwaiyu apa Kapaneam, taon k…®rik ye provins e Galili. K…®ni ye Sabat k…®rik, In ram…ôvhag k…®mi narmam…ô.  
\v 32 K…®ni narmam…ô k…®m…®s…ôr…®g n…ôgkiarien kafan, k…®m…®sakur k…®n, meinai n…ôgkiarien kafan, nanm…®n aik…®n.\x - \xo 4:32 \xt Mat 7:28-29 \x*   
\p
\v 33 K…®ni ye n…ôkwai nim…ô kape nofug…®nien, kw…ôn k…®rik aik…®n yame nanm…®n has ram…ôrer-p…ôn iran. K…®ni in rokr-apomh m…®m…ô,  
\v 34 ‚Äú!Eh, Yesu, yem…ô Nasaret! ?Rhawor? ?N…®mau…ô m…ô takoriah …ômaw…ô u…ô? Yakw…®rkun ta ik. !Ik yem…ô rhak…ô kape Kughen!‚Äù  
\v 35 M…ôr…®g Yesu r…®mn…ôgkiar skai k…®min m…®m…ô, ‚Äú!Ah, pim! !∆éta ye kw…ôn e!‚Äù Kw…ôn a ram…ôrer ye kwerkwan ir…ôri…ô, m…ôkneik…®n nanm…®n hah a r…ôsu…ô k…®n reiwaiyu mowhan ye n…®moptan…ô, map ta iran, k…®ni m…®p…ôh noriahyen in.   
\p
\v 36 K…®ni narmam…ô m-fam aik…®n a k…®sakur k…®n, mhani-p…ôn tuk …ôri…ô m…®n…ô mham…ô, ‚Äú!Eh! N…ôgkiarien p…®s…®n k…®rik e. Kw…ôn a kafan n…ôgkiarien nanm…®n aik…®n. Tukm…ô In r…ôgkiar k…®mi nanm…®n has m…®n…ô, kas…ôta ye narmam…ô.‚Äù  
\v 37 K…®ni n…ôvsaoyen kape Yesu r…®t…ôrhav markurao ye tan…ô a.   
\s1 Yesu r…®mnor huv…ô narmam…ô khapsaah  
\r (Mat 8:14-17; Mak 1:29-34)  
\p
\v 38 Aik…®n, Yesu rarar, m…®t…ôrhav ye nim…ô kape nofug…®nien m…®v…ôn apa nim…ô kape Saemon Pita\f + \fr 4:38 \ft  N…®p…®g k…®rik, kamokr…ôn k…®n Saemon Pita k…®m…ô, ‚ÄòSaemon.‚Äô K…®ni n…®p…®g k…®rik, kamokr…ôn k…®n k…®m…ô, ‚ÄòPita.‚Äô\f*. Ye n…®p…®g a, kuhu Saemon ramh…ô mam…ôpan p…®k, k…®ni iri…ô k…®saiyoh-p…ôn Yesu m…ô tukror huv…ô.  
\v 39 K…®ni Yesu r…ôrer ipak…ô tukun, m…ôgkiar skai k…®mi n…ôpanien, n…ôpanien r…ôta. Takt…ôkun …ôm…ô piahwaru a r…ôrer, m…®v…ôn m…®ruk ta n…ôri…ô n…ôv…®g…®nien.   
\p
\v 40 K…®ni n…®p…®g m…®rh natukriv…ô\f + \fr 4:40 \ft  N…ôm…ô Isrel, r…®kiri…ô r…®mn…ôs…®k m…ô Loa kape Moses ramni-…ôhu m…ô tukp…ôh n…®r…ôhyen yermam…ô ye Sabat. M…ôr…®g n…®p…®g m…®rh r…®m…®vi…ô, Sabat r…®nor infamien en, k…®ni k…®rkun n…®rh…ôyen yermam…ô.\f*, narmam…ô k…®mnhap…®k narmam…ô m-fam yam…ô m…®ne kamhamh…ô, mhav…ôn tuk Yesu. K…®ni In r…ôr…ôhu-p…ôn kwerm…®n ir…ôri…ô k…®rikian…ô k…®rikian…ô, k…®ni iri…ô m-fam k…®s…ôsan…®n.  
\v 41 K…®ni yarmh…ô m…®n…ô m…®n kamhat…ôrhav m…®sap ye narmam…ô khapsaah, m…®sokr…ôn apomh mham…ô, ‚Äú!Ik Ji Kughen!‚Äù M…ôr…®g Yesu r…ôgkiar skai k…®mi …ôri…ô m…ôtap…®g k…®n …ôri…ô tuk n…ôgkiarien meinai iri…ô kw…ônharkun ta m…ô In Kristo yame Kughen r…®mnher-p…ô k…®n.\x - \xo 4:41 \xt Mat 8:29; Mak 3:11-12 \x*   
\p
\v 42 K…ôni r…®kwamer k…®n, Yesu r…®t…ôrhav aik…®n a, m…®v…ôn apa ik…®n k…®rik. M…ôr…®g narmam…ô k…®m…®sarha-k…®n In, k…®ni n…®p…®g k…®m…®s…ôm, khau…ô tukun m…®sarkut mham…ô tukhani-…ôhu mham…ô In tukr…®p…ôh n…ôp…ôhyen …ôri…ô.  
\v 43 M…ôr…®g …ôm…ô Yesu r…®ni-p…ôn tuk …ôri…ô m…®m…ô, ‚ÄúN…®kam. Yo jakam…ôkeikei m…®v…ôn yerkwanu p…®s…®n p…®s…®n m…®n…ô, m…®ni-…ôrhav N…ôvsaoyen Huv…ô kape narmaruyen kape Kughen, meinai Kughen r…®mnher-p…ô k…®n yo m…ô jakor m…ôkneik…®n.‚Äù   
\p
\v 44 K…®ni In r…®mav…ôn mameriw…ôk ye tan…ô Judia mamni-…ôrhav n…ôgkiarien kape Kughen ye nim…ô kape nofug…®nien m…®n…ô.\x - \xo 4:44 \xt Mak 1:35-39; Mat 4:23\x*   
\c 5  
\s1 Aposol yam…ô m…®ne Yesu r…®mn…ôkup…ôn mokr…ôn k…®n …ôri…ô  
\r (Mat 4:18-22; Mak 1:16-20)  
\nb
\v 1 N…®p…®g k…®rik, Yesu r…ôrer ye n…®kar-kar nu ehu…ô kamni k…®m…ô Galili\f + \fr 5:1 \ft  N…ôgkiarien kape Gris ramni m…®m…ô, ‚Äúnu apa Genesaret.‚Äù\f*, k…®ni narmam…ô khapsaah k…®mnhau…ô m…®s…ôrer rarkurao iran mham…ô tuks…ôr…®g n…ôgkiarien kape Kughen.\x - \xo 5:1 \xt Mat 13:1-2; Mak 3:9-10 \x*  
\v 2 K…®ni In r…®mn…ôm kwaji rao k…®raru yame narmam…ô kape n…®viyen k…ôm…ô…ôm k…®mnhap…ôh kaw…ôrer ye n…®pak…®r m…®saikwas ye kap…ôri…ô net m…®n…ô.  
\v 3 M…ôkneik…®n Yesu ratp…ôn ye rao kape Saemon Pita, m…®ni-p…ôn tukun m…ô tukr…®vi-pir…ô rao. Saemon r…®vi-pir…ô rao, k…®ni Yesu r…ôkw…ôt…ô-p…ôn aik…®n mam…ôvhag k…®mi narmam…ô.   
\p
\v 4 Yesu r…®mn…ôgkiar infamien, k…®ni m…®ni-p…ôn tuk Saemon m…®m…ô, ‚ÄúSaemon, …ôsu…ô. P…ôh khav…ôn apa ik…ômn…®m, p…ôh naksaruk k…®n net m…®n…ô mhavi k…ôm…ô…ôm t…®ks…®n.‚Äù   
\p
\v 5 M…ôr…®g Saemon r…®ni-p…ôn tukun m…®m…ô, ‚ÄúYemehu…ô, yenp…®g, y…®m…®sarkut p…®k tuk nar e m…®seriaji reraan, m…ôr…®g y…®mnhap…ôh n…®viyen k…ôm…ô…ôm k…®rik. M…ôr…®g ik nakm…ô tukhav…ôn m…®n, ror p…ôn, p…ôh khav…ôn m…®saruk m…®n k…®n net m…®n…ô.‚Äù\x - \xo 5:5 \xt Jon 21:3-8 \x*   
\p
\v 6 Khavhir…ô, m…®saruk k…®n net m…®n…ô, mhavi k…ôm…ô…ôm khapsaah p…®k, ror net m…®n…ô kap…ôri…ô khakwar huv…ô k…®n k…ôm…ô…ôm, mharikakun m…®seikus net m…®n…ô.  
\v 7 K…®ni iri…ô k…®sokr…ôn-p…ôn k…®n iri…ô m…®n…ô t…®ks…®n ye rao m…®n k…®rik mham…ô tukhau…ô m…®sasitu ir…ôri…ô. K…®ni khau…ô m…®sarak…ô-p…ôn k…®n k…ôm…ô…ôm ye rao mir a kw…ôkrig, ipak…ô …ôm…ô rao mir kw…ômn…®m.   
\p
\v 8 K…®ni Saemon Pita r…®mn…ôm, k…®ni r…ôn…®mkur-p…ôn tuk Yesu mamni m…®m…ô, ‚ÄúYermaru. !Yuv…ôn isok tuk yo, meinai yo yakp…ôh n…ômhenien! Yo yor t…ôvhag…ô hah k…®rik.‚Äù  
\v 9 In r…®mn…ôgkiar m…ôknaik…®n meinai in m…®ne narmam…ô m…®n…ô a ye rao mir, k…®m…®sakur p…®k k…®n k…ôm…ô…ôm khapsaah yam…ô m…®ne k…®mnhavi.  
\v 10 K…®ni Jemes m…®ne Jon, ji Sebedi mir, yam…ô mir e kawor wok iris…®r Saemon, iriu m…®n k…®m…®wakur p…®k k…®n.  
\p M…ôr…®g Yesu r…®ni-p…ôn tuk Saemon m…®m…ô, ‚ÄúP…ôh n…®g…®nien. Ik yermam…ô kape n…®viyen k…ôm…ô…ôm. M…ôr…®g takt…ôkun ai mamv…ôn, ik takvi-p…ô narmam…ô.‚Äù  
\v 11 Ror p…ôn, k…®mnhavi-fiak kap…ôri…ô rao m…®n…ô, m…®s…ôp…ôh nar…®mnar m…®-fam mhakwas…®g …ôm…ô k…®n Yesu, k…®ni mhau…ô kafan narmam…ô m…®n…ô.\x - \xo 5:11 \xt Mat 19:27 \x*   
\s1 Yesu r…®mnor huv…ô yermam…ô k…®rik yame rav…ôh n…ômh…ôyen …ôut…ôn ye t…®kin\f + \fr 5:12 \ft  Ye N…ôkw…ôkw…ô kape Kughen, n…ôgkiarien e ‚Äòleprosi‚Äô ram…ôgkiar ye n…ômh…ôyen p…®s…®n p…®s…®n m…®n…ô kape t…®kim. N…ômh…ôyen m…®n…ô e kasoriah t…®kim, k…®ni Loa kape Moses ramni m…ô yermam…ô yame rav…ôh n…ômh…ôyen m…ôkna, in r…ômk…®m…®k ye n…®mr…® Kughen. ∆évheik…®n Levitikas yame rehu…ô 13-14.\f*  
\r (Mat 8:1-4; Mak 1:40-45)  
\p
\v 12 N…®p…®g k…®rik, Yesu r…®mneriw…ôk m…®v…ôn yerkwanu k…®rik, k…®ni kw…ôn k…®rik yame rav…ôh n…ômh…ôyen e leprosi, k…®ni n…®mh…ôyen ai r…®v…ôh fam n…®pran. K…®ni r…ôm Yesu, r…ôriw…ôk mu…ô tukun, meiwaiyu, m…ôn…®m-p…ôn n…®p…ôghig…®n ye n…®moptan…ô, k…®ni mamas…ôk …ôtg…®n Yesu m…®m…ô, ‚ÄúYermaru, tukm…ô nak…®rkun m…ô to nakor huv…ô yo, or huv…ô yo, m…ôspir ta n…ômk…®m…®k irak.‚Äù   
\p
\v 13 K…®ni Yesu r…ôrao-p…ôn m…®rap kw…ôn a, m…®m…ô, ‚Äú∆éw…ôh. Yakorkeikei m…ô jakor. !∆ésan…®n!‚Äù K…®ni takt…ôkun …ôm…ô n…ômh…ôyen e leprosi r…ôta.   
\p
\v 14 M…ôr…®g Yesu r…®m…®ni-…ôhu in m…®m…ô, ‚ÄúTakp…ôh n…®ni-…ôrhavyen nar…®mnar m…®n…ô e k…®mi narmam…ô. M…ôr…®g yuv…ôn m…ôm pris k…®rik p…ôh in r…ôm m…ô n…®pram r…®nor m…ôknen. K…®ni or sakrefaes k…®mi Kughen r…ôri-p…ôn yame Loa kape Moses r…®m…®ni ye yermam…ô k…®rik yame kafan leprosi ru…®rk…ôk, p…ôh narmam…ô tukharkun m…ô n…ôfrak…®sien nakwahuv…ô, k…®ni kafam n…ômk…®m…®k ru…®rk…ôk.‚Äù   
\p
\v 15 M…ôr…®g n…ôvsaoyen kape Yesu ramt…ôrhav mamv…ôn ik…®n m…®n…ô fam, k…®ni narmam…ô khapsaah kamhau…ô m…ô tuks…ôt…ôr…®g k…®n kafan n…ôgkiarien k…®ni mham…ô In tukror huv…ô n…ômh…ôyen m…®n…ô kap…ôri…ô.  
\v 16 M…ôr…®g, n…®p…®g r…®psaah, In ramv…ôn p…®s…®n …ôm…ô apa ik…®n k…®rk…ôk ik…®n, mam…ôhuak.   
\s1 Yesu r…®mnor huv…ô yermam…ô k…®rik n…®pran r…®mh…ô  
\r (Mat 9:1-8; Mak 2:1-12)  
\p
\v 17 N…®p…®g k…®rik, Yesu r…®mnhajoun apa nim…ô k…®rik, k…®ni Farisi m…®n…ô, m…®ne n…ômhajoun m…®n…ô kape Loa kape Moses, iri…ô kas…ôkw…ôt…ô m…®n aik…®n. K…®mnhas…®-p…ôn apa yerkwanu m…®n…ô apa provins mir e Galili, m…®ne Judia, m…®ne Jerusalem. K…®ni n…ôsan…®nien kape Kughen Yermaru ramar…ô tuk Yesu m…ô tukror huv…ô narmam…ô yam…ô m…®ne kamhamh…ô.  
\v 18 Ye n…®p…®g a, narmam…ô t…®ks…®n k…®mnhar…ôh kw…ôn k…®rik mhau…ô yame ramap…®r-p…ôn …ôm…ô ye n…®kaokao, meinai n…®pran r…®mh…ô. K…®ni iri…ô k…®sorkeikei m…ô tukhar…ôh m…®s…ôr…ôhu-p…ôn ye n…®hu Yesu.  
\v 19 M…ôr…®g k…®seinein m…ô tukshawor mhav…ôn im…ô, meinai narmam…ô khapsaah aik…®n. K…®ni k…®mnhav…ôn apa ye tokrei nim…ô, m…®s…ôhipu ta n…®kar nim…ô k…®rik, mhar…ôh n…®kaokao yermam…ô ramap…®r-p…ôn iran, mhavi, reiwaiyu-p…ôn ye kwerkwan ye narmam…ô, ipak…ô …ôm…ô tuk Yesu.   
\p
