\v 10 K…®ni kw…ônkwai grep r…®mhiak, k…®ni yemehu…ô kape plantesen rher-p…ôn k…®n kafan t…®ks…®n manaja m…ô tukhav…ôn m…®s…ôm narmam…ô yam…ô m…®ne k…®s…ôsim aik…®n m…ô tukhav…ôhsi-p…ôn grep nan, r…ômhen k…®n n…ôrok kafan.\x - \xo 20:10 \xt Aes 5:1-2 \x* M…ôr…®g iri…ô k…®sarar, mharapt…ôr…ôk…®n kw…ôn ai, m…®s…ôrk…®s-…ôrk…®s, m…®sher-p…ôn k…®n m…ô tukr…®rer…®g, mhap…ôh nhav…ôhsi-p…ônien mane k…®rik k…®min.  
