\v 18 M…ô narmam…ô m…®fam yam…ô m…®ne kamhar…ôh p…®k…®n s…ôpaag a, n…®k…®kriri…ô tukrakap…®r. K…®ni yermam…ô yame s…ôpaag a tukr…®mam…®r, mhopni, mhos…®s.‚Äù\x - \xo 20:18 \xt Aes 8:14-15; Rom 9:33; 1 Pet 2:8, 3:14\x*   
